{"title_page": "Mihai Raicu", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{short description|Romanian fencer}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name           = Mihai Raicu\n| image          = \n| imagesize      = \n| caption        = \n| birth_name     = \n| fullname       = \n| nickname       = \n| nationality    = \n| residence      = \n| birth_date     = \n| birth_place    = \n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n| height         = \n| weight         = \n| website        = \n| country        = \n| sport          = [[Fencing]]\n| event          = \n| collegeteam    = \n| club           = \n| team           = \n| turnedpro      = \n| coach          = \n| retired        = \n| coaching       = \n| worlds         = \n| regionals      = \n| nationals      = \n| olympics       = \n| highestranking = \n| pb             = \n| show-medals    = yes\n}}\n'''Mihai Raicu''' was a Romanian [[fencing|fencer]]. He competed in the individual [[sabre (fencing)|sabre]] event at the [[1928 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"sports-reference\">{{cite web |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ra/mihai-raicu-1.html |title=Mihai Raicu Olympic Results |accessdate=30 April 2010 |work=sports-reference.com}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Raicu, Mihai}}\n[[Category:Year of birth missing]]\n[[Category:Possibly living people]]\n[[Category:Romanian male fencers]]\n[[Category:Romanian sabre fencers]]\n[[Category:Olympic fencers of Romania]]\n[[Category:Fencers at the 1928 Summer Olympics]]\n\n\n{{Romania-fencing-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Romanian fencer}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name           = Mihai Raicu\n| image          = \n| imagesize      = \n| caption        = \n| birth_name     = \n| fullname       = \n| nickname       = \n| nationality    = \n| residence      = \n| birth_date     = \n| birth_place    = \n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n| height         = \n| weight         = \n| website